60
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,480
He also said

61
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,560
you don't need to go to the office today,

62
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,160
just stay home and rest well.

63
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,400
Okay.

64
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,800
I understand.

65
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,200
Yiran,

66
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:12,170
this is the tea you sent back last time,

67
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,460
it tastes really good.

68
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:25,920
Mr. Zhong.

69
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,760
What did you want to see us about?

70
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,420
Let me introduce you to

71
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,440
this is Li Yiran from Red Sail Capital.

72
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,159
Li Yiran.

73
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,280
Hello.

74
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,409
I'm Zhao Zi'ang.

75
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,200
Hi.

76
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,200
I'm Lin Xiaoxin.

77
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,720
Actually, it's nothing important.

78
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,880
First

79
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:46,280
I'd like to introduce Manager Li to you both

80
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,520
and second

81
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:51,240
it's about some matters concerning Chu Ruyun.

82
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:54,180
I'd like to ask for your help with something.

83
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,159
Of course

84
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,600
once it's done

85
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,560
there'll be plenty of benefits for both of you.

86
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,920
Chu Ruyun.

87
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,580
Manager Zhong.

88
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,200
What do you

89
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,640
want us to do?

90
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,280
Sir, who are you?

91
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,540
Hello, young lady.

92
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:49,440
I remember there used to be

93
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,000
a bridge over this river,

94
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,720
why can't I see it now?

95
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:56,560
Go about 200 meters that way and you'll see it.

96
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,600
Okay, thank you.

97
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:00,090
You're welcome.

98
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,200
Madam,

99
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,320
your phone call.

100
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:03,920
All right.

101
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:22,440
Just then, Chu Ruoyun received a call from her ex-boyfriend, Zhao Zi'ang.

102
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,440
Hey, Ruoyun.

103
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,040
Why are you calling me again?

104
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:28,000
I'm calling this time

105
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,520
specifically to apologize to you.

106
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:33,159
I've done many things that hurt you before,

107
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:34,640
can you forgive me?

108
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,640
Zhao Zi'ang,

109
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:40,200
just don't disturb my life anymore, that's all I ask.

110
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,720
No need to apologize. Let's leave it at that.

111
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,800
Ruoyun.

112
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,730
I'm not just calling to apologize,

113
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,560
I also have a secret to tell you.

114
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:52,760
Zhao Zi'ang,

115
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,520
you're trying to trick me with this kind of thing again.

116
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,000
No, Ruoyun.

117
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,640
I'm a dying man,

118
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,840
why would I lie to you?

119
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,240
Here's what happened.

120
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,760
Today Lin Xiaoxin came to see me

121
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:11,320
wanting to expose dirt on Long Haotian.

122
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:16,320
She gave me a lot of negative news about Long Haotian and Long Corporation.

123
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,960
I don't want to hurt you and Haotian anymore,

124
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,600
that's why I'm calling to tell you.

125
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,520
I have cancer,

126
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,520
terminal stage.

127
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:36,080
I'm just waiting to die at home now. I can't go anywhere.

128
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,400
If I weren't feeling so ill,

129
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,250
I would have brought it to you, Ruoyun.

130
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:47,000
Consider it seeing me for the last time,

131
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,440
just come over and get it.

132
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,840
I understand.

133
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,800
How did it go?

134
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,760
It's done.

135
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,920
So professional.

136
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,560
Look weaker.

137
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,360
Don't stick your butt out.

138
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,690
I'm not sticking it out.

139
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,000
Is this okay?

140
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,080
Yes, that's good.

141
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:27,800
It's fine,

142
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,160
definitely fine.

143
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:31,890
I'm going in.

144
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:32,960
Good luck.

145
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,520
Coming!

146
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,200
I'm here!

147
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,280
Please come in,

148
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,360
have a seat,

149
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,320
