150
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:02,050
My right foot isn't working well anymore.

151
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:08,210
What terminal illness do you have?

152
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,680
Bone cancer.

153
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,880
The doctor says I shouldn't walk much,

154
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,880
that's why I asked you to come over.

155
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,210
Can't it be treated?

156
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,480
The doctor says

157
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,080
it's too late for treatment.

158
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:26,480
Besides,

159
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,960
without you by my side,

160
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,760
life doesn't mean much to me anyway.

161
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:31,520
Let it be.

162
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,280
You said you wanted me to come get some documents.

163
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,140
Where are they?

164
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,680
Right,

165
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,200
I forgot.

166
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:00,080
Making things up.

167
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,650
These are just slanders against Haotian.

168
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,180
I don't believe it,

169
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,480
but as these lies spread,

170
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,160
even falsehoods

171
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:10,490
can eventually become truth, can't they?

172
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:14,320
Thank you.

173
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,930
I'll take these to Haotian right away.

174
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:22,960
Ruoyun.

175
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:24,560
Let's

176
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,060
have one last embrace,

177
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,530
to bring closure to our relationship.

